283
00:20:50,130 --> 00:20:51,890
Hej, čo sa deje?

284
00:20:52,370 --> 00:20:54,340
Prečo sa pozeráš dole?

285
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:57,070
Si celá červená v tvári.

286
00:20:57,070 --> 00:20:58,650
Máš teplotu?

287
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:02,940
Je studená.

288
00:21:04,850 --> 00:21:06,310
To nie je dobré.

289
00:21:06,310 --> 00:21:10,790
Keďže som zombie, tak aj keď to robím, nedokážem rozoznať rozdiely v teplotách.

290
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:19,540
Mama.

291
00:21:24,840 --> 00:21:25,550
Mama?

292
00:21:26,840 --> 00:21:27,460
Nie...

293
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:30,610
T-To nič.

294
00:21:30,610 --> 00:21:31,610
Hej, počkaj.

295
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:35,870
Mero-chan, zabudla si si tu veci...

296
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:45,900
Rea-dono, je mi to veľmi ľúto.

297
00:21:47,690 --> 00:21:50,130
Tak, hotovo.

298
00:21:50,130 --> 00:21:51,470
Poďme urobiť večeru.

299
00:21:52,740 --> 00:21:57,330
Prečo som to vtedy povedala...

300
00:21:57,890 --> 00:22:01,840
Každopádne som isto niečo cítila...

301
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,280
To je zombie?

302
00:22:05,280 --> 00:22:07,200
Aká krásna osoba.

303
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,750
To je riadne klamstvo, že?

